    "slug": "optimistic-by-default",
    "title": "Optimistic by Default",
    "excerpt": "React 19's useOptimistic makes the Like button feel instant.",
    "content": "The Like button on each post uses React 19's useOptimistic hook. The count updates the moment you click, while the Server Action persists the change to disk in the background.\n\nIf the server write fails, React rolls the optimistic value back automatically.",
    "coverId": "1035",
